Class MergedCardChangeSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.events.transport.MergedCardChangeSet

  • public final class MergedCardChangeSet
extends Object
    Contains data for a Card created during a merge operation, plus source information from the original Card in its host Item.

    4.0
